task.summary: Added while loops and if statements. Also added file name arguments.
Added if statements, object creation, object method calls, converted to java only.
Added conversions into ASM code for creation and adding ints, methods and classes.
Added storing of variables to JVMCompiler for testing.
Added storing of variable IDs to reference variables to perform operations to.
Project structure tidied up and unused code removed.
Generate bytecode for while loops and if statements.
Added different code generation depending on operator for if statements.
Added instantiation of objects and calling of instance methods.
Added constructor parameters to class block and a constructor block that has all blocks added that are within a class but not a method/within a method.
Cleaned up code and removed unneeded output and execute method. Added package parser and block.
Added importing of classes when creating instances. Also added using of package when calling instance methods.
Tidied up code by replacing tokens with Strings. Added use of package directory if a variable is the same type as the class it is defined within. Import directory is used otherwise.
Added unit testing. Removed the original TokenizerTest class.
Added IfParser test and CommentParser test.
